      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON. ¶ John Shirley Esqr, of Brisbane, Queensland ¶ a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially to ¶  Lichenolog...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">89.09.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates, 1887-90.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Form completed and signed by M; other supporters’ autograph signatures. Given the Society’s summer recess, the form could have been transmitted at any time from about April to September 1889; it is dated to the last likely date. </p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">John Shirley Esqr, of Brisbane, Queensland</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially to</seg> Lichenology</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">being desirous of becoming a Fellow of the </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">, we, whose names are underwritten, beg leave to recommend him to that honour.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller M.D., FLS</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">C. S. Wilkinson, F.L.S., F.G.S.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">W. Woolls Ph.D., F.L.S.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">This recommendation must be signed by Three or more Fellows.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.B. – The Christian name of the Candidate must be stated at length, as well as his Residence, and any special qualifications he may possess.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society, on the</seg>
               <seg> </seg>7st<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">The numerals in the date have been altered, with</seg> 7 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">written over</seg> 21.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg>
               <seg> </seg>November 1889.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">The Ballot will take place on the 5th day of December 1889.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated back</seg>: John Shirley | elected 5 Dec 1889 | not joined 9/9/90 [<seg style="font-style: italic; ">i.e. did not pay his fees</seg>]<seg style="font-style: italic; ">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
